Microsoft FlexiBenefits
Spending account
As part of your benefits package, you can use your 2% Flexi Fund to reimburse employee-only, wellness-related expenses through the Spending Account.
Any funds you haven't used to top up your core benefits or select from the choice benefits will automatically transfer into your Spending Account. All you need to do is choose from the wellbeing categories and claim back the expenses through Flexi Benefits.
You can make a claim at any time of the year* - so you could buy some home exercise equipment in the January sales, treat yourself to a wearable fitness tracker, claim back the fees for your personal tax advisor, take regular classes - in yoga, painting or photography, or music lessons and claim back throughout the year. You can also use in conjunction with the discounts available through Perks at Work and Headspace.
This year we're offering broader categories of reimbursable items and services, intended to be relevant, inclusive and cover a larger range of life and career stages to support your physical, mental and emotional, and financial wellbeing.
Visit Flexi Benefits to learn more about how to claim.
* deadline for 2022 claims is 24 December
